a_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9st","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7686,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-never-says-no-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Charity: The Prophet never refused to give in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was never asked anything for which he said no. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5687, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2311 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0637\u064f\u0651 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/06\/prophet-frees-marries-safiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees Safiyyah, marries her","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, emancipated Safiyyah, married her, and regarded her freedom as her dowry. The Prophet held a banquet with sweet dishes. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4798, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1365 Grade: Muttafaqun\u00a0Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/31\/miracle-prophet-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet&#8217;s miracle of providing water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 31, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during the afternoon prayer and people were asking for water to perform ablution, but they could not find it. Some water was brought to the Prophet and he placed his hand in the vessel\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/10\/musa-moses-patience-harm\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Musa: Moses hurt by people, but was patient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity when a man from the Ansar said, \u201cBy Allah, Muhammad did not intend to please Allah with this!\u201d I came to the Prophet and told him about it, then anger could be seen on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/26\/no-gift-better-than-sabr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: No gift better than patience, resilience","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: Some people from the Ansar asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he gave them. Then they asked for charity again and he gave them. Then they asked again and he gave them until all he had was gone. The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6183,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/10\/greet-peace-do-not-know\/","url_meta":{"origin":36361,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Greet strangers with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: A man asked the Prophet, \u201cWhich Islam is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThat you feed the hungry and you greet with peace those you know and those you do not know.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 28, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 39 Grade:\u20